('predis-ai', 'Predis.ai', 'AI-powered social media content generator and scheduler',
 'Predis.ai uses artificial intelligence to generate social media posts, captions, and visuals from a single prompt. Enter your product description or URL and Predis generates ready-to-publish content for Instagram, Facebook, LinkedIn, and Twitter. The platform includes a built-in image editor, competitor analysis, and scheduling features. Content teams use Predis to cut social media production time by 70% without sacrificing brand consistency. The AI learns your brand voice over time and improves output quality with each use. Competitor analysis shows what is working in your niche so you can benchmark your content strategy against rivals. The scheduling calendar provides a week-at-a-glance view of your planned content across all platforms.',
