('supergrow', 'Supergrow', 'LinkedIn growth tool powered by AI for founders and creators',
 'Supergrow combines AI content generation with LinkedIn growth strategies in one platform. It analyzes your profile, benchmarks against top creators in your niche, and generates personalized post templates proven to drive engagement. The AI repurposes your existing content - blog posts, videos, tweets - into LinkedIn-native formats automatically. A built-in carousel maker converts text into swipeable visual slides. Supergrow also tracks your follower growth, post performance, and suggests optimal posting times based on your audience behavior. The hook analyzer scores your post openings and suggests improvements to stop the scroll before readers see the rest of your content.',
