('vista-social', 'Vista Social', 'Modern social media management with AI features for growing teams',
 'Vista Social is a modern social media management platform built to replace legacy tools like Hootsuite at a fraction of the cost. It supports 11 networks including TikTok, YouTube, Google Business Profile, and Pinterest. AI features include a caption generator, best-time-to-post recommendations, and an automated content recycler that resurfaces evergreen posts. The review management feature aggregates mentions and reviews from multiple sources into a single inbox. Agencies and growing teams use Vista Social for its clean UX and transparent pricing compared to Sprout Social and Hootsuite. The listening feature monitors keywords and brand mentions across social platforms, giving teams a real-time view of what is being said about their brand without needing a separate social listening tool.',
